&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead and mentor a team of data engineers, driving their technical growth and professional development.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Champion the vision and execution of scalable data processing systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with product and engineering teams to consistently define data architecture and solution strategies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Foster a strong technical community by developing close relationships amongst Engineering Managers.&lt;/li&gt;
