&lt;p&gt;This leader drives customer-centric roadmaps and translates vision into measurable outcomes that perform in the field. You will partner closely with Engineering, Sales, Customer Experience, Threat Intelligence, and Marketing to ensure Dragos delivers differentiated, high-impact products that solve critical customer problems globally. You will champion customer advocacy and ensure your team is deeply embedded in discovery, delivery, and ongoing iteration across the portfolio.&lt;/p&gt;
