&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;5+ years in a production software development environment, with 2+ years of experience with Python development.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1+ years of experience designing and maintaining CI/CD pipelines using tools such as Jenkins, GitLab CI, GitHub Actions, or similar.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with containerization technologies (Docker, Kubernetes) and infrastructure-as-code (Terraform, Ansible, or similar).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with cloud platforms (AWS, Azure, or GCP) and cloud-native services.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated ability to design and build developer tooling and workflow automation that improves team productivity.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency with git work

